gov.usgs.anss.fetcher

Class NEICFetchConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.anss.fetcher.NEICFetchConfig

  • public class NEICFetchConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    This is an all static class that sets up the requeststation, and channel gaptypes for Q330 stations, Reftek stations, and EdgeStations at the NEIC. It is unlikely this code is useful elsewhere as it contains many reference to host names at the NEIC.
